{"word":"G2064 - ἔρχομαι - érchomai - er'-khom-ahee - Accompany","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">érchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">er'-khom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Accompany</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வா, பிரவேசி"},{"paragraph":"to come"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice of a primary verb (used only in the present and imperfect tenses, the others being supplied by a kindred [middle voice] word, <b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> <b>eleuthomai</b> or <b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B8;&#x03C9;</b> <b>eltho&#x0304;</b>; which do not otherwise occur); to <i>come</i> or <i>go</i> (in a great variety of applications, literally and figuratively): - accompany, appear, bring, come enter, fall out, go, grow, X light, X next, pass, resort, be set.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1330/1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525/1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831/1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904/1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064/2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922/3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928/3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022/4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281/4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334/4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905/4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565/565\">G565</a>"}]}